  "text": "In these 23 studies, nearly all the mean duration of effect was more than 6 months except one study that did not report the details of follow-up time [CITATION_1] and two articles had short follow-up time [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] . Noticeable, 11 studies had more than 10 months of mean duration of effect, and the effect time even lasted more than 20 months without recurrence in some patients [CITATION_4] . Generally, BTXA injection is an effective treatment with a long-lasting effect for FS.",
